links.title: Regeneron, Gilead Rise As Therapies Used To Treat President
links.description: The decision by President Donald Trump's doctors to treat his Covid-19 infection with drug therapies from Regeneron Pharmaceuticals ( REGN) and Gilead Sciences ( GILD) gave the drug companies a weekend of heavy publicity. It also boosted REGN stock and GILD stock in early trading Monday.
